@@TJvErrorBlinkStyle
<TITLE TJvErrorBlinkStyle type>
Summary
  The type used for the BlinkStyle property in an error provider component.
Description
  TJvErrorBlinkStyle defines the allowable values for the BlinkStyle property in TJvErrorProvider. TJvErrorBlinkStyle
  can have one of the follwing values:
@@TJvErrorBlinkStyle.ebsAlwaysBlink
  The error icon is always blinked on and off.
@@TJvErrorBlinkStyle.ebsBlinkIfDifferentError
  The error icon is only blinked if the error message has changed since the previous blink.
@@TJvErrorBlinkStyle.ebsNeverBlink
  The error icon is never blinked.
